PrecisAppointment of WILLIAM REID of Fall River, Nova Scotia, to be a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of Prince Edward Island to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years.
